{"tid":1694623,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"街坊們出街   一定要飲多幾樽水","createTime":"2019-11-05T08:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T09:16:55.000Z","uid":30862,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ee56ba0689c904d1f4f2955d514d8ad7b5708cdf","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:34:46.000Z","msg":"眼見愈來愈多街坊夜晚出街<br />\n感覺到大家都進化緊<br />\n嗌得愈來愈大聲<br />\n哨亦都愈來愈精準<br />\n又識be water<br />\n好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係！！！！<br />\n嗌極都會口渴架嘛<br />\n所以一定要帶定幾樽野飲傍身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">凈係得把口 係唔夠架咁多位街坊！！</span><br />\n<br />\n以下將會幫埋大家分類 <br />\n希望大家都會帶埋出街飲啦<br />\n請人飲都得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlevel 0: 樽裝水<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ax05yh8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fax05yh8.png&h=2fdd690c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n方便輕身 解渴一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係樽身軟左d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlevel 1: 紙包飲品<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uYM4OYg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuYM4OYg.png&h=95e1d055&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好多花款 任君選擇<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係唔小心跌落地 就好易會爆開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跣親人就唔好啦 </span><br />\n<br />\nlevel 2: 罐裝飲品<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bGaAVD3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbGaAVD3.png&h=1d697663&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VriiTsL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVriiTsL.png&h=b4c30586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n細細罐好易袋 係重左少少既<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但勝在夠硬凈</span> 分分鐘硬過骨頭架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlevel 3: 酒類飲品<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jaTCpAU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjaTCpAU.png&h=f71d9b4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s1LtwfY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs1LtwfY.png&h=6ed54bd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢排大家都好大壓力 好需要chill chill<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但好多酒都係玻璃樽裝<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心輕放吖 碎左就好危險架啦</span><br />\n<br />\nlevel max: 保溫湯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZSLX83G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZSLX83G.png&h=d18bc540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天氣咁凍 最好就自己煲定d湯水出街飲啦<br />\n個壺咁硬身 你想煲咩飲都得架<br />\n暖下個身都好吖嘛<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但記得唔好整咁熱吖<br />\n太熱 辣親個口就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n大家落街唔好再兩手空空啦<br />\n起碼見到狗/有街坊比狗咬 除左得把口<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">仲可以企高少少 望多d野 飲多幾啖水</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一齊進化啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我會做多一步 帶野飲出街<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：繼續大嗌 用把口就夠"},{"pid":"1aef463c0004236d9da3417b231d5c5879f3c468","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:35:00.000Z","msg":"我要飲水"},{"pid":"f43d444e82c52d73ff63d5f03fc2615f9afc931a","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:35:19.000Z","msg":"請人飲又得"},{"pid":"7cef6a04047862be083a71c51ff0450af519b362","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:35:36.000Z","msg":"進化啦街坊<br />\n唔好再得把口"},{"pid":"bdade02d733a4e3342090d043bc6d84ddb962bd2","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:35:58.000Z","msg":"打狗<br />\n救人"},{"pid":"d76f80ffb4d70e12de4dbde5ddec7227c24f9377","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:36:16.000Z","msg":"反抗從來都唔只係一句口號"},{"pid":"a865f043df9430250d95dbcd90a295dafdd955e6","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:36:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23b5b5ccc6fa9e56ac586d4bea5c2c9d03cb0624","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:36:54.000Z","msg":"兩手空空 <br />\n其實係得比狗咬"},{"pid":"c0af2cc5f2129723cbf5974716b956d85e3246fd","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:37:19.000Z","msg":"得把口真係唔得架...."},{"pid":"f29710193317453e5445baa59d595912632c27f0","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:37:33.000Z","msg":"一齊進化啦街坊<br />\n<br />\n草木皆兵"},{"pid":"b5d5794534f46297e33e9bdbaf337fdfc7bbafb2","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:38:01.000Z","msg":"推上去比所有街坊睇！"},{"pid":"2f761057a6821f475aff276fa72de5201d7216f7","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:38:39.000Z","msg":"請幫手推上去啦"},{"pid":"2a20214f22bbe22fa1bc9fb9c623d13596e1fd89","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:39:00.000Z","msg":"推爆吖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要比多少少準備"},{"pid":"35398b38f60512acd04aaf2aeaa10d5135fe6d4d","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:39:10.000Z","msg":"唔係唔推下話"},{"pid":"44e575b471d06ec95d4c5129dbbcdcf141fc4d17","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:39:32.000Z","msg":"唔該大家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔可以得把口"},{"pid":"6454be7e6605dabed0a6221551650ef98b6c1d22","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:39:56.000Z","msg":"全部人唔該帶多幾樽水出街！"},{"pid":"53a26016afb25211f49f68598002542f010a34ae","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:40:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ccc4b8d6eccba53b275ad6459f120943664fe882","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:41:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf40fc0983489eb0d75fd292905983e91f1c3747","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:41:27.000Z","msg":"一路睇杜生一路推"},{"pid":"6cb3b23604da9be56f84126a2b4d7a316bb9d5b5","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:41:38.000Z","msg":"唔該大家"},{"pid":"9361537fd35e12d354cb81387386ee52c9ff25c2","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:42:02.000Z","msg":"推爆"},{"pid":"73032447e8e36b6901c6f3177a4a8a8bf9ef06bb","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:42:25.000Z","msg":"唔該大家 帶多幾支"},{"pid":"49c458294c557b903c269d54845452425f24bdd3","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:42:51.000Z","msg":"唔好睇阿叻啦 哂時間"},{"pid":"5fd3f048e4c26208e0a707d71f6fc421ee78d089","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:43:07.000Z","msg":"推返戰術post"},{"pid":"9816c0a8a60bf1b42fa68cf5f74959f95e619611","tid":1694623,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:43:18.000Z","msg":"唔該大家"}]}